<i>noun</i>: 폭격 [폭껵] <br>
<ul>
<li><i>noun</i><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>폭격 [폭껵]</dt><br>
<dd>bombing; bombing attack</dd><br>
<dd>비행기에서 폭탄을 떨어뜨려 적의 군대나 시설 등을 파괴하는 일.</dd><br>
<dd>An act of dropping bombs from a combat plane, destroying the troops, facilities, etc., of an army.</dd><br>
</li>
</ul>